BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:l0nMO7B6UWffFwpxbQdqA
SUMMARY:French festival
DTSTAMP:20260321T221841Z
DTSTART:20260322T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle Center (1 mile NW)\n\nFrench Fest is a celebration of F
	rench-speaking culture\, with art\, live music\, dancing\, films\, wine ta
	sting\, a baguette tasting contest\, vendors\, and sustainability workshop
